fix: add cascade soft-deletes and notifications to all deletion paths

- New cascadeCancelShifts() primitive in admin-actions.ts
- deleteEvent now cascades: EventDays, EventResources, Shifts, Bookings
- deleteResource now cascades: EventResources, Shifts, Bookings
- unassignResourceFromEvent now cascades: Shifts, Bookings
- deleteUser now cascades: Shifts/Bookings, PushSubscriptions, eventId
- All paths send email + push notifications to affected users
- Updated UI confirm dialogs and cascade summary messages
- Updated tests for new return types and mock delegates
